                <note rend="inline" type="source">Edward M. House Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Wilson</persName> to Colonel
                            <persName type="to">E. M. House</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-03-03T15:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">March</hi> 3, 1919—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3. I will come directly to Brest and Paris as you think best. Advise.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Woodrow Wilson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
